T1  - Are buybacks back? Menu-driven debt reduction schemes with heterogeneous creditors
AU  - Diwan, Ishac
AU  - Spiegel, Mark M.
JO  - Journal of Monetary Economics
VL  - 34
IS  - 2
SP  - 279
EP  - 293
